dct_title_s: Marin County, California land and water parcels, 2009
dct_description_sm:
Land and water parcels in Marin County, California, 2009. A parcel is a fundamental
        cadastral unit: a piece of land which can be owned, sold, and developed. Parcels have legal
        descriptions that describe their boundaries and contain information concerning rights and
        interests. Data are a graphic representation of parcel boundaries in Marin
        County.
